"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"relative pt-32 pb-16 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-24 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hotshot Outfitters Michigan hunting and charter fishing guide team in Port Hope, Michigan\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-40\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmichigan-hunting-charter-fishing-outfitter-about.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-pine-deep/70 via-pine-deep/65 to-pine-deep\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5 lg:px-8\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"text-ember text-xs tracking-[0.4em] font-display mb-4\">ABOUT HOTSHOT OUTFITTERS</div><h1 class=\"font-display text-6xl lg:text-8xl tracking-wider leading-[0.95]\">MICHIGAN OUTFIT.<br/><span class=\"text-ember\">MICHIGAN BONES.</span></h1></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 lg:py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 lg:px-8 space-y-6 text-mist text-lg leading-relaxed\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p>Hotshot Outfitters is based in Port Hope, Michigan — a working town on the Lake Huron shoreline, deep in the heart of Michigan&#x27;s Thumb. We run full-service guided hunts year-round and Lake Huron charter fishing trips once the ice clears the bays.</p><p>We&#x27;ve been doing this for more than twenty years. That&#x27;s not a marketing line. That&#x27;s the actual number of seasons we&#x27;ve walked these woodlots, sat these blinds, set these decoy spreads, and ran these waters. The dirt knows us. The lake knows us. And when you book with us, you get the benefit of every one of those seasons.</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl tracking-wider text-bone pt-4\">WHAT WE GUIDE.</h2><p>Whitetail deer, wild turkey, duck, goose, coyote and fox, cottontail rabbit, and crow — across the fields, marsh edges, and hardwood lots of Huron County, Michigan. When Lake Huron opens up, we run charter fishing trips out of the Port Hope area. Same outfit. Same standards.</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl tracking-wider text-bone pt-4\">HOW WE WORK.</h2><p>Full-service. We handle stand placement, calling, decoying, retrieves, boat, electronics, gear — all of it. You bring a valid Michigan hunting or fishing license, weather-appropriate clothing, and your own personal equipment if you prefer it.</p><p>We don&#x27;t run a high-fence operation. These are real Michigan hunts on real Michigan ground. Some days the woods cooperate. Some days they don&#x27;t. Twenty-plus years has taught us that the only thing we can promise is that we&#x27;ll put you in the best spot we&#x27;ve got and work as hard as you do to make it happen.</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-4xl tracking-wider text-bone pt-4\">WHERE WE HUNT.</h2><p>Michigan&#x27;s Thumb is a stretch of the state that gets quietly overlooked by hunters chasing the big-name destinations up north. We think that&#x27;s a mistake. The combination of working farms, river-bottom hardwoods, marsh edges along Lake Huron, and the sheer amount of private ground we&#x27;ve built relationships with over twenty years makes Huron County one of the best-kept secrets in the Great Lakes. We hunt it every season because there&#x27;s no place we&#x27;d rather be.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 lg:py-20 bg-pine border-y border-ember/10\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"border-l-2 border-ember pl-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award text-ember mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg><div class=\"font-display text-3xl tracking-widest mb-3\">20+ YEARS</div><p class=\"text-mist text-sm leading-relaxed\">Two decades guiding Michigan hunts and Lake Huron trips. Experience that earns itself.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"border-l-2 border-ember pl-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-compass text-ember mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m16.24 7.76-1.804 5.411a2 2 0 0 1-1.265 1.265L7.76 16.24l1.804-5.411a2 2 0 0 1 1.265-1.265z\"></path></svg><div class=\"font-display text-3xl tracking-widest mb-3\">MICHIGAN-BORN</div><p class=\"text-mist text-sm leading-relaxed\">Port Hope, Huron County, the Thumb. We don&#x27;t just hunt here — we live here.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"border-l-2 border-ember pl-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-crosshair text-ember mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"22\" x2=\"18\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"2\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"2\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"22\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg><div class=\"font-display text-3xl tracking-widest mb-3\">REAL HUNTS</div><p class=\"text-mist text-sm leading-relaxed\">Working farms, woodlots, marsh edges. No high-fence shortcuts.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 lg:px-8 text-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-5xl lg:text-7xl tracking-wider mb-6\">LET&#x27;S TALK.</h2><p class=\"text-mist text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8\">Easiest way to get a feel for the outfit is to pick up the phone. We&#x27;ll answer your questions and tell you straight whether we&#x27;re the right fit.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-3\"><a href=\"tel:+19895514551\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-7 py-4 bg-ember hover:bg-ember-deep text-bone font-display text-xl tracking-widest transition\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 